Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't sleep again, huh bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now, you gotta get some sleep \Nor you'll go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up. Hey, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:01:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But why didn't you get any body parts back \Nafter you beat that creepy fox?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search and kill \Ntill I get it all back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been pushing yourself too hard \Nsince we left the land of Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't gotten any rest, \Nbeating monsters left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't last for long like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You, who threatens the peace of this land, \Nare a demon to us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need a papa or a mama to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:18.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,許してください！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:22.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしは…そなたを…救えませぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:38.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…また眠れないのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:40.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神を…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:43.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだって！ちゃんと寝ないと頭が参っちまうぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:46.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,って…おい！あにき、ちょっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:50.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待ってくれって！おっ…あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:01:01.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もわかんねーよな。\Nあの化け狐の鬼神やっつけたのに身体が戻らないってのがさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:04.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戻るまで探して斬る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:06.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そりゃ…そうだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:11.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただなあにき。醍醐出てから無理しすぎだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:15.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ろくに休みもしねーでやたらめったらバケモンやっつけ回って。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなんじゃ身体が持た…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:19.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うっ！てて…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:26.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今や国を脅かす兄上こそ、この国にとっての鬼神！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:32.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしは…そなたを…救えませぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:34.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:40.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃんとおっかちゃんがいなくたって…生きてけらぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきにはおいらがついててやっからな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:46.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兄貴！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light \Nin the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices \Nin the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light \Nin the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices \Nin the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,#13 The story of the Blank-faced Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Where's that at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Past those mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever been to one? \NIt's a natural hot bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You could get some rest there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot springs ease fatigue and \Nmake you feel better. Mama said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... Anyways, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He said a monster was seen near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Asakura army has retreated, \Nand our land is blessed with rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The deal with the demons still stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But for how much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me. \NYou're not my wife, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So this isn't the right face either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect place \Nto spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You rest up here. I'm going \Nto gather some firewood and berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be a bad guy's hideout \Nso be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't kill anyone! \NJust kind of beat 'em up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There. That should be about enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A waterfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...! Oh, it's just a huge Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't taste good so you don't want \Nto eat me. Besides, my bro will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Your mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, it's me, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pull so hard now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is she a ghoul? \N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A human then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-I can't tell. \N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Okaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You live here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The pilgrims who come \Nto the waterfall give me food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That waterfall, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, why doesn't that Buddha \Nhave a face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it goes a long way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A Buddha statue carver  \N came to the waterfall one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He found an eroded boulder in the shape of \NFudo, a wise but fearsome deity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That carver was originally famed  \N for making kind-faced Buddha statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But as wars raged on, people began to want \Nstatues with the fierce face of Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so they forgot about that carver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to get back at everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and began carving a Fudo statue \Ninto the boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He carved the body, hands, and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But as he started on the face, \Na thought struck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to carve  \N a magnificent face like none other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All he could carve  \N were faces he'd seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For years and years,  \N he carved and destroyed over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The carver grew old,  \N still unable to carve a satisfactory face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He died in his chagrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're too young to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This rice porridge reminded me of my mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You called me your mama, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look like her that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like her twin. \NEven your voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, he's fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been sleeping well these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you let him sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets cold at night around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh dang it, \NI've never had such good food before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:11:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I call you Mama...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, I thought it'd be easier to say \Nthan Okaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You sweet little child, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel safe now, \Nand it's making me sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I was worried \Nthe drug wasn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,About that carver. \NThat wasn't the end of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After that carver died,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,a vengeful spirit began to live \Nin that Fudo statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To settle the carver's old scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It wanted a face ever so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fudo revived the carver \Nand ordered him to bring live humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So it could take their faces for itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I am that carver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can look into people's souls and \Nchange my face and voice to suit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A child's face wouldn't do for the Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But that man's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You sweet little child, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I give your face \Nto the Fudo then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, bro. I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tie you up, \Nso why didn't you just run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ever let you take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Step away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Never! I promised I'd stay by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You slept pretty soundly, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that, Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done enough. \NThere's no need to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice, it's bro's mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Okaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't my face changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never seen your mother's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face... Give me your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting forever \Nfor a face like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I must have his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The most magnificent I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be so magnificent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it enough to have eyes, a nose, \Nand a mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you had to be so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You became a monster that \Ntricks people and tears off their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about how those people \Nwho've had their faces torn off feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Their pain, their frustration, \Ntheir sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A face, more magnificent \Nthan any other Fudo statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why have I...? I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when have I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me feel your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What a kind child you are, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your smiling face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like... the face of Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've been more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you mixed up in trouble \Nand reminded you of your mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always the one saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll save you whenever you need me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I got clumsy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot spring. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What... Hey, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, about that monster \Nnear the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-I just... \N-Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I've never been in one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look! \NI mean, I know you can't see, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch, all my cuts sting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but it feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be what heaven's like, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So it may not be a bad idea \Nto just hurry up and die, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Priest. \NWhere did you rise up from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak as if I just rose up from hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was here before you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We must be destined to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, bath time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bath time! \N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. \NThey're more like monkeys than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive them, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where you from? \N-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-Haven't seen you around. \N-Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Traveling? Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going somewhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... We haven't decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro is just bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, stop looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Isn't this a map? \N-A map?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a map!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-A map! \N-Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Stop staring at my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, come on. Let us see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop it! \N-Come on, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え？それってどこにあんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの山の向こうさね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんがと！おっちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:34.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,温泉だってよ温泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知ってるか？山とかに勝手に湯が湧いてんだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこならあにきもゆっくり休めると思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:45.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,温泉は身体だけじゃなくて気分も落ち着くっておいらのおっかちゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:49.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…まぁ、とにかく行こうよ。な？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:57.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その温泉の近くにバケモンが出たってさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:11.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,朝倉も退け…こうして恵みの雨も降る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:38.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今はまだ…鬼神との約定は反故になっておらん。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:43.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…このままでは、いずれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,離せ！てめぇ女房じゃねぇな！離せってんだい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！離せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何しやがる…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:50.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やはり…この顔も違ったか！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,りゃ夜を越すのにちょうどいいや！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:11.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきは休んでてくれよな。おいらは薪と木の実でも取ってくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:16.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ、それとここ…野党の根城かもしれないから気をつけてくれよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも殺しちゃダメだ！とっちめるだけだぜ？な？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:28.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よっと。へへ。けっこう集まったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:33.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん？滝の音？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげぇや！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:56.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な、なんでい！？でっけぇ仏像かい…脅かすな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:57.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊や？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:05.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おお、おいら喰ってもうまくねぇぞ！？それに百鬼丸のあにきが！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…おっかちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私が…かえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら…どろろだよ？おっかちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう、そんなに引っ張ったら痛いって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！この人を見てくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやかしかい？\N違う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人か…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わからない\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あたしはおかかってモンだえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんで、ここはあたしの家だえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかかは1人で住んでんのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:14.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ときどき滝に来る行者さんたちが食べ物を置いてってくれるから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食べていけてる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さっきの滝かぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:21.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういやぁ、あの仏像なんで顔がないんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:26.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えっ…あぁ、それは随分と前の話になんだけども
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,昔、とある仏師がの滝へ行ってきて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:36.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,滝の水で不動のような形に削られた岩を見つけたんだえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:42.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,元々その仏師は、穏やかな顔の菩薩を彫ることで評判だった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:48.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けれど、侍の時代になると人々は力強い顔の不動を求め…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その仏師は忘れられていったんだえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仏師は皆を見返そうと、
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その岩に不動を彫りはじめた。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,身体、手、足。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:01.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,最後に顔を彫るとき、仏師は思った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:06.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それまで見たどの不動よりも立派な顔を作ってやると。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:07.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けれど…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:13.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,できる顔はどこかで見たようなものばかり。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:18.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何年も何年も彫っては壊し彫っては壊し
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:23.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やがて仏師は歳をとり、とうとう顔を作れないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:26.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無念の中で死んでしまったんだえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんか…よくわかんねー話だなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:32.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろにはまだ難しかったかね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わっ！うまそう！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さ、どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いっただっきまー！あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:43.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:47.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お粥見てたら…おっかちゃん思い出しちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:51.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういや、あたしをおかちゃんって呼んどったね？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなに似とるのかえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そっくりもそっくりだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:01.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どっからどう見てもおいらのおっかちゃんだ！声だって！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ…いけねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あらら、寝てしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここんとこ、ろくに寝てなかったからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,起こさないでやってくれるかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:22.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここらは夜になると冷えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:35.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちっくしょう！こんなうめぇメシ初めてだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:43.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ…そう。よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ごっそさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…あの…さ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:50.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、その…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱり…お…お…おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:11:01.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,って呼んで、いい…かな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:07.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかかちゃんよりおっかちゃんのほうがいいかな…って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,甘えんぼさんだえ、どろろは。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ええよ、好きに呼んだらええ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へへ…おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:34.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,安心したらなんだかおいらも急に\N眠くなって…きた…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:38.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そう。薬が効くか心配したけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:41.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何のことだい？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:46.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さっき話した仏師の話には続きがあるんだえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その仏師が死んでしまったあと、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:56.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その不動はいつしかあやかしが取り憑いてしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:59.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仏師の無念を晴らそうとね。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,顔が欲しい顔が欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:08.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,不動は仏師を蘇らせ、生きた人間を連れて来るよう命じた。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その顔を不動に与えるために
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:16.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仏師とはあたしのこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:22.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,不動の力で相手の心を読めば、好きなように顔も声も変えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子供の顔は不動には合わない…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:29.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けれど、あの男の顔なら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,甘えんぼさんだねぇ、どろろは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待って…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:10.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならばその顔を不動に与えてやろうか！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:24.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待ってろ、あにき…おいらが助けてやっからな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:47.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ来た！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:48.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきを…返して…わっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:59.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,縛らないでおいてやったのに、なぜ逃げなかった！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:01.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:10.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あにきは絶対…渡さねぇぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この…離れな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:18.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,離れるもんか！あにきにはおいらがついてるって…誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ずいぶん寝てたな…あにき
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おやめなさい。百鬼丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:45.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうよいのです。何も傷つける必要はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの声…あにきの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さ。母の元においで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:56.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は…おかかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なっ！どうして…どうして顔が変わらぬ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:05.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前…母の顔を知らぬのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,顔を…顔をおよこし！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:21.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ずっと…ずっと探し続けたその顔を！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうやめてくれ！おっかちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:29.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,黙れ！あたしは、あいつの顔が欲しいんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今までで一番立派な顔が！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでそんなに立派じゃなきゃダメなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,目があって鼻があって口がありゃ充分だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それをおかかは自分勝手に…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:45.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人を騙して顔剥ぎ取るバケモンになっちまったんじゃねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バケモン…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんで…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:51.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでそんなことしてんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:56.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分の顔取り上げられちまったモンの気持ち考えてみろよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:02.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,辛くて…悔しくて…悲しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:17.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,立派な顔…どの不動よりも立派な…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:21.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ…なぜ…わからない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつから？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつから…あたしは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無理だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:38.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私には、もう…無理だえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,か、顔に…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,か、顔に…笑っておくれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:35.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,優しい子だえ…どろろは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたの笑った顔、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:45.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仏様のように…見える…わけだえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ごめんよあにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらがしっかりしなきゃって思ってたのに。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:29.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余計なことさせちまったり、思い出させちまったり…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:33.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、いっつもあにきに助けてもらってばっかだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:36.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきが困ったときには絶対に！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ってぇ…へっ、
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,またドジしちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:42.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺は大丈夫。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,温泉、行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え…ちょ、ちょっと！待ってくれよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:20:01.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あのさ。温泉の近くにバケモンが出るってやつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,嘘なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,つい…なんていうか\N行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ、あにき！ここだここだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:19.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら入んの初めてだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:26.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,み、見んなよあにき！見えねぇのは知ってるけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,う…だから見んなって！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いてて…傷にしみるけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うわぁー、気持ちいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:40.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,極楽ってこんな所かもな。あにき
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うわぁー、気持ちいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:48.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だったらさっさとくたばるのも悪くないね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ば…バケモン！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さん！どから湧いて出てきた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ずいぶんな言われようだねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さんたちが来る前からいたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったく、これも腐れ縁かねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わぁ、風呂だ風呂だー！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おふろー！\Nそれっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいおい…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何しやがんだ！こんチクショー！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:26.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こら！すまんのう、そこらの子猿と変わらんでな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:28.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,許してやってくれ\N来たん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前、どから来たん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:34.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この辺りじゃ見ねぇな\N見ないね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらたち、ずっと旅してんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:39.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,旅？どこまで行くんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:41.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どっか行くんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:45.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなの…まだ決まってねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その人、お兄さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきはあにきだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:52.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、何？これ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:55.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の背中、何か描いてあるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:01.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なっ、何言ってやがんだ！ジロジロ見んな！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:04.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これ…地図ってやつじゃないかなぁ\N地図？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:06.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,地図！地図だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉ！そうだ！これ地図！絶対！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,地図だー！\Nもっと見せてくれよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:15.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うるせー！人の背中いつまでもジロジロ見んなー！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:18.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えーいいだろー？見せてくれよー！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:21.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁんでー？見ーせーて！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love \Nthis accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world \Non our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hakumenfudo"
